807
01:19:54.838 --> 01:19:56.588
[panting]

808
01:20:27.796 --> 01:20:29.796
[both grunting]

809
01:20:40.671 --> 01:20:41.546
[groans]

810
01:20:53.671 --> 01:20:55.880
