Then you can fall.

813
01:21:19.963 --> 01:21:20.796
Hmph.

814
01:21:21.963 --> 01:21:23.171
It's for your daughter?

815
01:21:24.421 --> 01:21:25.713
She can't use it anymore.

816
01:21:26.880 --> 01:21:29.213
