827
01:24:00.880 --> 01:24:01.713
Mai.

828
01:24:02.796 --> 01:24:03.630
Mom.

829
01:24:06.005 --> 01:24:06.880
Are you okay?

830
01:24:09.130 --> 01:24:12.505
