860
01:26:04.296 --> 01:26:06.421
Team One stays here on standby.
the rest follow me.

861
01:26:06.505 --> 01:26:07.338
Roger that.

862
01:26:45.755 --> 01:26:47.380
This is for my brave daughter.

863
01:26:49.380 --> 01:26:50.421
Wait for me.

864
01:26:57.630 --> 01:26:58.463
Mom?

865
01:26:59.880 --> 01:27:00.713
Mom?

866
01:27:09.963 --> 01:27:11.963
[brakes squeaking]

867
01:27:18.171 --> 01:27:19.005
Boss.

868
01:27:20.588 --> 01:27:21.421
Boss.

869
01:27:23.130 --> 01:27:23.963
Boss.

870
01:27:45.296 --> 01:27:46.213
[gunshot]

871
01:28:36.838 --> 01:28:38.463
[man muttering]

872
01:28:51.713 --> 01:28:52.963
[gunshot]

