874
01:29:15.838 --> 01:29:17.005
Clear the area.

875
01:29:17.463 --> 01:29:19.921
Check all the vehicles.

876
01:29:21.838 --> 01:29:22.921
Mom!

877
01:29:29.588 --> 01:29:32.463
